message: Hello! Thank you for chatting with Better Deal Insurance today. My name is Chris. How can I assist you?
Finally, I've been waiting forever. My name is John, and I need help with my policy.
Of course, John. I'm here to help. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name?
Thank you for completing security. Can you please provide your date of birth?
That's all correct. To further assist you, can you confirm your first line of address and postcode?
Great, thank you for completing security, John. How can I help you with your policy today?
I've been trying to make a claim for the past week, but I keep getting errors on the website. This is frustrating!
I completely understand the frustration, John. Let me see what I can do to help resolve this for you. Please allow me a moment to look into this.
Thank you, I appreciate it. This whole situation has been a nightmare.

I'm here to help, John. It looks like there might be a technical issue on our end. A possible resolution could be to escalate this matter to our IT department for further investigation. How does this sound to you?
I just want to get this sorted. Yes, please escalate it. I need to make this claim as soon as possible.
Thank you for your understanding, John. I've escalated the issue to our IT department. They will reach out to you shortly to assist further. Is there anything else you'd like to address today?
No, that's all for now. I hope the IT team can fix this fast.
I'm glad we could help, John. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
